A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%B1u-T%E1%BA%B1ng/%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-giang/poem-NDJsdyK0YC0TNzcx_mLrWQ">Đồng giang - 桐 江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%B1u-T%E1%BA%B1ng/author-nWUL33GiLZTfwhmyICj7Cw">Vương Hựu Tằng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Nam-tr%C3%AC/poem-Mq0TBpDYXDCXmoqTx6zGEw">Nam trì - 南池</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/S%E1%BB%9F-ki%E1%BA%BFn-h%C3%A0nh/poem-7zX_fvrqSHORA8aiuARZQw">Sở kiến hành - 所見行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/S%E1%BB%9F-t%C6%B0-%C4%90%E1%BA%AFc-Thai-Ch%C3%A2u-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-t%C6%B0-h%E1%BB%99-Ki%E1%BB%81n-ti%C3%AAu-t%E1%BB%A9c/poem-gMDFuXMZ6HJeB9ywElo18g">Sở tư - Đắc Thai Châu Trịnh tư hộ Kiền tiêu tức - 所思－得台州鄭司戶虔消息</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn-t%C4%83ng-Ti%E1%BB%81m-ki%E1%BA%BFn-t%E1%BA%B7ng/poem-hz8hbWcAgwn0l_l-89-sBw">Thứ vận tăng Tiềm kiến tặng - 次韻僧潛見贈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br></div>	</div>
